Compute the natural logarithm of the number.



```js
ln(num: number) -> number
```

### Tags

* `math`

### Examples

```js
const exampleSketch = startSketchOn("XZ")
  |> startProfileAt([0, 0], %)
  |> line([ln(100), 15], %)
  |> line([5, -6], %)
  |> line([-10, -10], %)
  |> close(%)

const example = extrude(5, exampleSketch)
```
